{"tid":2512220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"1個星期3日假，不過工時長，定係一般工時，2日假?","createTime":"2021-05-01T13:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T14:43:39.000Z","uid":286199,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"55fd4b3f2e8876dd96f254d99261ec588aeb3ceb","tid":2512220,"uid":286199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:39:59.000Z","msg":"嚟緊轉新工，做西廚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1日15個鍾，兩個半鐘落場，包3餐，3     日假一個星期<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1日12個鍾，兩個半鐘落場，包3餐，2日假一個星期<br />\n<br />\n3日假好似正好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又可以搵一日炒散，1個月抽4日炒散都好撚fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過又驚唔夠訓比人sack，野都冇力扑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日日射精左3、4年，黑眼圈深到好似比人打左兩拳咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />驚冇得日日c伏會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3日假真係好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望自己適應到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7670ea122e04d0bf7affc988e61e4d9b930ada7c","tid":2512220,"uid":286199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:42:20.000Z","msg":"廚房佬冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b195e73cb6096a3f49395bd3f3209e394138134f","tid":2512220,"uid":286199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:43:15.000Z","msg":"3日假係咪者係可以陪多d女朋友，同佢一齊可以有quality time<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f144201153aeb8f0